            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, slice the onions finely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> 1-2 tbsp of vegetable oil to a large pan on a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the onion and a pinch of both the sugar and salt to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reduce</strong> the heat to a medium-low and cook for 20-25 min, or until crispy and brown, stirring occasionally (lowering the heat to prevent burning)</p>",
